---
title: Halloumi, Pepper and Sweetcorn Tacos with Chipotle Mayonnaise
description: Big on flavour but short on prep, these 20-minute vegetarian tacos are about to steal the dinnertime limelight. Perfect for entertaining, or treating yourself midweek, pile them high with spoonfuls of sweetcorn & peppers, golden brown halloumi and a dollop of chipotle mayo. Taco Tuesdays have never looked so delicious.
